quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  26,10,"(Rántí) nígbà tí Olúwa rẹ pe (Ànábì) Mūsā pé: \"Lọ bá ìjọ alábòsí"
  26,11,ìjọ Fir‘aon (kí o sì sọ̱ fún wọn) pé 'Ṣé wọn kò níí bẹ̀rù (Allāhu) ni
  26,12,"Ó sọ pé: \"Olúwa mi, dájúdájú èmi ń bẹ̀rù pé wọ́n máa pè mí ní òpùrọ́"
  26,13,"Ó sì máa jẹ́ ìnira fún mi (tí wọ́n bá pè mí ní òpùrọ́). Ahọ́n mi kò sì já gaaraga. Nítorí náà, ránṣẹ́ sí Hārūn"
  26,14,"Àti pé mo ní ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ kan lọ́rùn lọ́dọ̀ wọn. Nítorí náà, mò ń bẹ̀rù pé wọ́n máa pa mí"
  26,15,"(Allāhu) sọ pé: \"Rárá (wọn kò lè pa ọ́). Nítorí náà, kí ẹ̀yin méjèèjì mú àwọn àmì (iṣẹ́ ìyanu) Wa lọ (bá wọn). Dájúdájú Àwa ń bẹ pẹ̀lú yín; À ń gbọ́ (ọ̀rọ̀ yín)"
  26,16,"Ẹ̀yin méjèèjì, ẹ lọ bá Fir‘aon. Kí ẹ sọ fún un pé: 'Dájúdájú àwa ni Òjíṣẹ́ Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá"
  26,17,(À ń sọ fún ọ) pé kí o jẹ́ kí àwọn ọmọ ’Isrọ̄’īl máa bá wa lọ
  26,18,"(Fir‘aon) wí pé: “Ṣé kì í ṣe ní ààrin wa ni a ti tọ́ ọ ní kékeré ni, tí o sì gbé ní ọ̀dọ̀ wa fún ọdún púpọ̀ nínú ìṣẹ̀mí ayé rẹ"
  26,19,O sì ṣe iṣẹ́ ọwọ́ rẹ tí o ṣe (sí wa). Ìwọ sì wà nínú àwọn aláìmoore.”
  26,20,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: \"Mo ṣe é nígbà náà nígbà tí mo wà nínú àwọn aláìmọ̀kan ni"
  26,21,"Mo sì sá fun yín nígbà tí mo bẹ̀rù yín. Nítorí náà, Allāhu ti ta mí lọ́rẹ ipò Ànábì. Ó sì ṣe mí ní (ọ̀kan) nínú àwọn Òjíṣẹ́"
  26,22,Àti pé ìyẹn ni ìdẹ̀ra tí ò ń ṣe ìrègún rẹ̀ lé mi lórí. Pé ó sọ àwọn ọmọ ’Isrọ̄’īl di ẹrú (ńkọ́)
  26,23,"Fir‘aon wí pé: “Kí ni Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá?”"
  26,24,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: “(Allāhu ni)"
  26,25,"(Fir‘aon) wí fún àwọn t’ó wà ní àyíká rẹ̀ pé: “Ṣé ẹ ẹ̀ gbọ́ ọ̀rọ̀ (t’ó ń sọ ni)?”"
  26,26,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: “(Allāhu ni) Olúwa yín àti Olúwa àwọn bàbá yín, àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́.”"
  26,27,"(Fir‘aon) wí pé: “Dájúdájú Òjíṣẹ́ yín èyí tí wọ́n rán si yín, wèrè mà ni.”"
  26,28,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: “(Allāhu ni) Olúwa ibùyọ òòrùn, ibùwọ̀ òòrùn àti ohunkóhun t’ó ń bẹ láààrin àwọn méjèèjì, tí ẹ bá máa ń ṣe làákàyè.”"
  26,29,"(Fir‘aon) wí pé: “Dájúdájú tí o bá fi lè jọ́sìn fún ọlọ́hun kan yàtọ̀ sí mi, dájúdájú mo máa sọ ọ́ di ara àwọn ẹlẹ́wọ̀n.”"
  26,30,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: “Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé mo mú kiní kan t’ó yanjú wá fún ọ ńkọ́?”"
  26,31,"(Fir‘aon) wí pé: “Mú un wá nígbà náà tí ìwọ bá wà nínú àwọn olódodo.”"
  26,32,"Nítorí náà, ó ju ọ̀pá rẹ̀ sílẹ̀, ó sì di ejò pọ́nńbélé"
  26,33,"Ó tún fa ọwọ́ rẹ̀ yọ síta, ó sì di funfun fún àwọn olùwòran"